| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0174 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8c18d266-57c9-5ab9-8ffb-8a5d46602315"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
